::Aerotaur::
       He finally covers the final distance to catch up with flicker and 
lands between him and Nightlight.  "Nightlight, run.  NOW!"  He puts his arms 
and wings out to his side, thus making both an effective screen and a sign 
that he was unarmed.  "Don't you understand Flicker.  To Rodimus, no Maximal 
is expendable."

--part1_141.e22a335.2bb9f992_boundary
